>美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJuEF0r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJuEF0r.gif&h=a8c24eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=af2ec9ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"2c25b89b8f120e5141f07ecb2de67194e352b815","tid":1544514,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"爆滿唔好落車都玩躝啦"},{"pid":"6b5e491470be3d0f907b3ef18ad990f49cab91f3","tid":1544514,"uid":41355,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好咁做呀！<br />\n旅客上唔車，出入唔到機場就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋人數最緊要，人多就安全架啦～"},{"pid":"0cfc680af4ca0fb13564558a8e3230d00e98a62f","tid":1544514,"uid":63303,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好，朝朝早六點幾E車都已經爆棚，機場員工返唔到工好大鑊，飛機有機會delay"},{"pid":"b73331e4f7072cc6602c99655d71687e00f28779","tid":1544514,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a45a5062e5ca652d8d1282baaf23f6f3ff411f18","tid":1544514,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c5be5121becc2e8cb8c958b3e2b3d514e35656","tid":1544514,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:31.000Z","msg":"9月1話俾你知，有用。諗下點解嗰日1330就已經停S線"},{"pid":"bde187492